      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ECHOES OF DAD (1) Finished on top last time at Angle Park and proven performer at this distance. Should come to hand quickly. Neil Rawlings kennel are having a great run of late. Will take plenty of beating. BROTHER ERNEST (2) Good effort to finish 2nd last time at Angle Park in 30.66s over 530m. Will be motoring home late. Placed at every start this preparation. Looks suited and should just win this. GUNNING BANDIT (9) Handy enough when winning last start at Mount Gambier and suited at this trip in the past. Maintaining a perfect record the last 3 starts. TAKE A LITTLE (10) Ran 3rd last time at Mount Gambier and will be well suited at the trip. Very competitive this campaign and demonstrating upward trajectory in recent races.",
